# vim-hoogle-web


## Introduction

Search by hoogle web.

## Requirement

* `curl` command
* `+timers`
* `+job`
* Vim version 8.0 or above

## Installation

[Neobundle](https://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim) / [Vundle](https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim) / [vim-plug](https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug)

```vim
NeoBundle 'osyo-manga/vim-hoogle-web'
Plugin 'osyo-manga/vim-hoogle-web'
Plug 'osyo-manga/vim-hoogle-web'
```

[pathogen](https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen)

```
git clone https://github.com/osyo-manga/vim-hoogle-web ~/.vim/bundle/vim-hoogle-web
```


## Setting

```vim
" open command
let g:hoogle#web#open_cmd = "split"
```

## Usage

```vim
:Unite hoogle/web:map

:Unite hoogle/web:\:\:a
```


